# UI Enhancements & Notifications Plan

This plan addresses reported issues with Batch/Delete operations, Health Score display, and implements a new notification system for WhatsApp and Telegram.

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] Data Model & Business Logic

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Add `whatsappNumber` (String?) and `telegramId` (String?) to the `Workspace` model.
- Add `notificationTypes` (String[]?) to track which events trigger notifications (e.g., REPLIES, MEETINGS).

#### [MODIFY] [campaign.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/backend/src/services/campaign.service.ts)
- Implement `bulkDeleteCampaigns(ids: string[])` to handle multiple deletions efficiently.

#### [NEW] [notification.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/backend/src/services/notification.service.ts)
- Create a service to handle WhatsApp (via Twilio) and Telegram (via Bot API) notifications.
- Include methods like `sendNotification(workspaceId, message)`.

#### [MODIFY] [scheduler.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/backend/src/services/scheduler.service.ts)
- Update [pollForReplies](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/backend/src/services/scheduler.service.ts#26-83) to trigger `NotificationService.sendNotification` when a new reply is detected.

---

### [Frontend] UI & UX Improvements

#### [MODIFY] [campaigns/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/frontend/src/app/campaigns/page.tsx)
- Add multi-select checkboxes for campaigns.
- Implement a "Bulk Delete" button that appears when campaigns are selected.

#### [MODIFY] [settings/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/frontend/src/app/settings/page.tsx)
- **Health Score**: Improve visibility by adding a color-coded status indicator and making the numeric score more prominent.
- **Notifications**: Add a new section under "Profile & Security" or a dedicated "Integrations" tab to configure WhatsApp/Telegram alerts.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test `bulkDeleteCampaigns` to ensure all related data (leads, events) is correctly handled.
- Mock `NotificationService` to verify that triggers in [SchedulerService](file:///c:/Users/tasmi/OneDrive/agentic%20workflow/notebookllm/backend/src/services/scheduler.service.ts#24-422) work as expected.

### Manual Verification
- Verify multi-select and delete functionality in both Campaigns and Leads pages.
- Confirm Health Score displays correctly for various mailbox states.
- Test notification settings by updating phone/telegram details and manually triggering a "mock" reply.
